## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="14e30-114">Il <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> costruttore inizializza la <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> proprietà.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="14e30-114">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor initializes the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="14e30-115">L'identificatore deve essere univoco all'interno di una grammatica specificata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="14e30-115">The identifier must be unique within a given grammar.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="14e30-116">Il <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> costruttore genera un <xref:System.FormatException> nelle circostanze seguenti:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="14e30-116">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor throws a <xref:System.FormatException> in the following circumstances:</span></span>  

